MTY Muncipal Income Tax Yield
#### Description
Numerical vector of length 11194. details in [Ultsch/Behnisch, 2017; Thrun/Ultsch, 2018].
#### Usage
data("MTY")

#### Examples
```{r}
data(MTY)
str(MTY)
```
